-- Citi hires Emmanuel from UBS as MD for Asia FIG
-- 
-- Sun Apr 3, 2011 10:51pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/04/us-citi-emmanuel-idUSTRE7330CS20110404

 

 HONG KONG  (Reuters) - Citigroup Inc ( C.N ) has hired Jeff Emmanuel from UBS AG ( UBSN.VX ) as managing director of its Asia-Pacific financial institutions group (FIG), Citigroup said in a statement on Monday. 

 Emmanuel will be responsible for Citi's FIG businesses in Australia and New Zealand (ANZ) and will report to Chris Knoblanche and Tony Osmond, respective heads of ANZ global banking and investment banking, and Simon Yoo and Jing Zhao, heads of FIG Asia-Pacific. (Reporting by  Denny Thomas ; Editing by Chris Lewis)